import {HorizontalGridLines, LineSeries, XAxis, XYPlot, YAxis} from "react-vis";

export const Graph = () => {
    return (
        <XYPlot
            width={1500}
            height={300}>
            <HorizontalGridLines />
            <LineSeries
                data={[
                    {x: 1, y: 10},
                    {x: 2, y: 11},
                    {x: 3, y: 9},
                    {x: 4, y: 11},
                    {x: 5, y: 1},
                    {x: 6, y: 2},
                    {x: 7, y: 3},
                    {x: 8, y: 4},
                    {x: 9, y: 1},
                    {x: 10, y: 2},
                    {x: 11, y: 3},
                    {x: 12, y: 4},
                ]}/>
            <XAxis />
            <YAxis />
        </XYPlot>
    )
}
